{
  "stem": "24268.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It changed dramatically, but systematically, not immediately.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could feel the fear, you could feel the terror, and they grabbed people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, they put families to our home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our family, because of our-- our-- we had the space, whenever they could they brought in from different places, from different towns.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they add the family to our-- to give up the one room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then another, the one who lost the husband, the young couple, the [INAUDIBLE], she got another family, her own, her sister with-- two sisters, actually-- with husband and two nieces.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it start to be already a very frightening situation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Matter of fact, my brother, when my mom wanted to save him in '32, so he went in hiding with one of the roommates who we'd been helping to get the diploma in engineering school.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He went to [INAUDIBLE] and he spent there a couple weeks, or 10 days, I don't recall how long.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now he helped him, my brother helped him to get his diploma, the engineering diploma.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then after, when the war broke out, he found out anyway that he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he was nice, and I think as gratitude, he offered-- he stayed there for a short while.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the situation, then did-- also, the situation got gradually bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were not allowed to walk in the streets anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not in the Main Street anyway, and they allowed to make like on a big [? field ?] [? separate ?] [INAUDIBLE] I remember they called it [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they made like everybody who ever lived there-- we didn't because we lived in suburb-- but the people who lived in Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
